# MirrorMe is configured inside the extension (no env vars needed to use it):
# open the extension's Settings page to add your Gemini API key and photos.
#
# The only (optional) build-time variable, for extension developers who want a
# stable extension id across machines — see README → Development:
#
#   extension/.env.local:
#   VITE_CRX_PUBLIC_KEY=   # base64 DER public key (openssl, see README)
